       <p>or on the Emergency Information Line:<br> (213) 740-9233</p> 
       <h5>To Report an Emergency:</h5> 
       <p>Call the USC Department of Public Safety</p> 
       <p><strong>University Park campus:</strong><br> (213) 740-4321</p> 
       <p><strong>Health Sciences campus:</strong><br> (323) 442-1000</p> 
